time it would take pakistan to field nuclear weapons from a matter 
of months to a matter of weeks several sources said 
bombmaking requires enriching uranium hexafluoride a gas then 
solidifying it into a metal that is milled into a hollow sphere for 
use as a bomb core pakistan already has taken some of those steps 
the sources said 
