its not too early to begin celebrating pbs 
10th season of the woodwrights shop where host roy underhill 
illustrates the ancient craft of woodworking with traditional 
american tools and a dry hip wit 
no power tools please 
its the difference between playing a stradivarius and a 
synthesizer underhill said both of them get the work done 
but theres a lot of difference in the playing and what you end up 
with the product is the process 
the 10th season premiere oct 20 features a rocking horse 
modeled on those of germanys franconia region where underhill 
shot two other shows that feature the districts traditional 
