its those secrets that speak to underhill he reveals them on 
his show patiently working the wood with his crafts traditional 
tools he explores reveals and connects with something basic and 
profound about humankind 
this is the fundamental stuff part of us since our ancestors 
started banging rocks on trees he said its fundamental to 
