earned 9 to 10 an hour while she made 550 and had more 
seniority 
it makes me mad very mad said voeltner an 11year johnson 
veteran a lot of women out there are losing 100 a week in 
takehome pay thats a lot of money when youre trying to raise a 
family 
other women say theyve been stripped of their dignity 
virginia green a bennington vt worker was 50 and long done 
with childbearing when she was transferred to a glorified laundry 
job was i angry youd better believe it she said she 
considered sterilization but said her doctor told her it was too 
