bush announced the speech himself at a meeting with a group of 
business leaders as the white house launched a major effort to sell 
the bipartisan package unveiled on sunday 
earlier he met with a group of skeptical and undecided 
republican house members some participants at the meeting said 
that several lawmakers urged bush to give a televised address to 
the nation 
